::Shredder::

Shredder emerges from the jungle, nearly tripping over Mantella. He bends 
down, putting a hand on her shoulder and flipping her over. She was in stasis 
lock, and obvioustly needed a CR chamber.

Shredder lifts Mantella to his shoulder, flying off toward the Destron base.
